instanceVariables.Dialogue: It's important to start a fire before dark. Look in the field guide for some tips on how to collect wood and start a fire.

instanceVariables.Dialogue2: Great job! You started a fire! Now it's time to find water. Look in the field guide for more information on finding good water sources.
instanceVariables.Dialogue: This looks like a good place to build a fire. Stand here to start a fire using the technique from the field guide.
instanceVariables.Dialogue3: Hmm it doesn't seem like this wood will light on fire. Check the field guide for tips on finding good firewood.

instanceVariables.MushroomDialogue: Now that you've found water and started a fire, you can look for some food. Check the field guide for some tips on safely foraging for food.

instanceVariables.Dialogue: Looks like you found a good source of water, great job! Before you drink your water, make sure you check the field guide for some important tips on how to make sure your water is safe to drink.
Do want to boil or drink the water?
instanceVariables.Dialogue2: Drinking water before it is sanitized can hurt your health! Check your field guide to learn how to safely drink water.
instanceVariables.Dialogue3: Great! Place this water over the fire to sanitize it before drinking!
